# ─── NBA Live Stats (balldontlie.io) ─────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Without this key the app runs with static snapshot data (still fully functional).
# To enable auto-updating live stats:
#
#   1. Sign up FREE at https://app.balldontlie.io/register  (no credit card)
#   2. Copy your API key from the dashboard
#   3. Create a file called  .env.local  in the project root and paste:
#
#        VITE_BDL_API_KEY=your_key_here
#
#   4. Restart the dev server — the app will fetch real NBA stats automatically.
#      Stats are cached for 4 hours in localStorage; the player-ID map is cached
#      permanently (IDs never change).
#
# Free tier limits: 60 requests/minute — more than enough for this app.

VITE_BDL_API_KEY=
